(
<emphasis id="C2E42EAE0C00A0136A80037AC18C0383" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="137">Holotype</emphasis>
: CEPEC barcode CEPEC 15308!; 
<emphasis id="C4C26F2976AD0C5171E35EC3D8C17E8D" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="137">isotypes</emphasis>
